The paper focuses on tracking the evolution of software changes on mailing lists, which is a key aspect of software engineering (cs.SE). The method presented in the paper involves identifying semantically similar changes, which could fall under programming languages (cs.PL) or information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also mentions the use of the method for certifiability and conformance to processes, which could relate to cybersecurity (cs.CY) or cryptography (cs.CR).
